com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.os
Interface WindowsOperatingSystem

All Superinterfaces:
com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.Capability, com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.DeployModelObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OperatingSystem
All Known Implementing Classes:
WindowsOperatingSystemImpl
public interface WindowsOperatingSystem
extends OperatingSystem

A representation of the model object 'Windows Operating System'.

The following features are supported:

  • Company
  • Domain Admin
  • Domain Name
  • Domain Password
  • Encryption Level
  • Install Date
  • Language
  • Language Group
  • Last Boot Up Time
  • Machine Object OU
  • Number Of Licensed Users
  • Owner
  • Product Key
  • Product Type
  • System Drive
  • Windows Directory
  • Workgroup Name

See Also:
OsPackage.getWindowsOperatingSystem()
